{"tid":2351639,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"SM家族「線上演唱會」流出站長現場飯拍　粉絲嚇傻：怎麼進去的？","createTime":"2021-01-03T11:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T14:54:12.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"171a2386ff850f8a27b273c0ff268434cdd50f27","tid":2351639,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T11:38:35.000Z","msg":"南韓三大經紀公司之一的SM娛樂，在元旦舉行《SMTOWN LIVE &quot;Culture Humanity&rdquo;》家族演唱會，破天荒免費開唱，希望在全球疫情肆虐之際，給粉絲帶了安慰的力量。由於是線上播出，現場並未開放觀眾，沒想到事後卻出現站長「在現場」的飯拍，令粉絲傻眼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5373/d5373840.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5373%2Fd5373840.jpg&h=f8001197&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲SM家族演唱會，aespa成員Winter演出的「播出畫面」。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／SMTOWN）<br />\n<br />\n由於疫情的緣故，此次SM家族演唱會僅以線上模式播出，現場沒有開放粉絲。沒想到事後網路上，竟出現旗下新人女團aespa的成員Winter的飯拍影片，從拍攝角度看來，拍攝者是在現場，某些鏡頭還出現遮蔽物，看起來是躲在某處拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5373/d5373815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5373%2Fd5373815.jpg&h=fa775abc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲SM家族演唱沒有開放粉絲，卻出現aespa的成員Winter的飯拍影片。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n這組影片釋出後，讓許多粉絲相當驚嚇，紛紛留言質問：「你是誰？為什麼可以在裡面拍攝？」、「是現場工作人員嗎？可以允許你們把影片放到網路上？」、「你是怎進去的？」更有人痛罵這種行徑根本是私生飯、跟蹤狂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5373/d5373818.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5373%2Fd5373818.jpg&h=61724f6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲SM家族演唱沒有開放粉絲，卻出現aespa的成員Winter的飯拍影片。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n雖然也有人表示，由於aespa是新人團體，公司可能會為了讓她們被更多人認識，默許「站長」可以入內拍攝，但這說法也被反駁，「怎麼來說都是疫情期間，說故意放站長進去太不合理了吧。」、「這甚至是該頻道第一支影片呢！SM有可能放莫名其妙的人進去，只因為對方說自己是站長嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5373/d5373841.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5373%2Fd5373841.jpg&h=34aa1109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5373/d5373831.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5373%2Fd5373831.jpg&h=50cb7cc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c1d91c642cafd8fab3320722dd02670cdc0063d","tid":2351639,"uid":271835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T11:44:58.000Z","msg":"無碼流出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723983efe6ff3662af3dc522d2e83d6444951de8","tid":2351639,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T11:49:57.000Z","msg":"某會然<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf480dc8ff4597dbddad6063b107e15d6bf4f19","tid":2351639,"uid":3405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T11:55:25.000Z","msg":"你點影的"},{"pid":"e26c89c1052107f92119fef791a7143e513b916d","tid":2351639,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T12:32:50.000Z","msg":"其實係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ef812e00025aaa2faa9eb49cf60725ec703ca8","tid":2351639,"uid":27597,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T12:33:55.000Z","msg":"你點影的"},{"pid":"db0923274b337eb043b3b568c6c2293f32ae7928","tid":2351639,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T14:54:12.000Z","msg":"咁癲應該係牙邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}